# Petni Chat - Frontend Setup

## Installation

```bash
npm install
```

## Environment Variables

Create a `.env` file in the `client` directory:

```
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
REACT_APP_WS_URL=http://localhost:5000
```

## Development

```bash
npm start
```

Runs the app in development mode at [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000).

## Build

```bash
npm run build
```

Builds the app for production to the `build` folder.

## Features

- Real-time anonymous chat with strangers
- Gender-based matching (ভূত ↔ पेत्नी only)
- Audio & Video calls
- Emoji reactions and message replies
- Shop for buying Magical Stones
- Avatar customization
- Chat history
- Admin moderation dashboard
- Dark mystical theme with purple accents
- Mobile responsive
- PWA installable

## Pages

- **Home** - Landing page with stats
- **Chat** - Real-time 1v1 chat
- **Auth** - Login/Register
- **Shop** - Buy stones and avatars
- **History** - View past chats
- **Settings** - Profile & security
- **Admin** - Moderation dashboard

## Components

- **Navbar** - Main navigation
- **Footer** - Site footer
- **AuthPage** - Login/Register forms
- **ChatPage** - Chat interface
- **ShopPage** - Stone packages & avatars
- **HistoryPage** - Chat history viewer
- **SettingsPage** - User settings
- **AdminDashboard** - Moderation panel

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS for utility-first styling
- Custom dark theme with purple accents
- Responsive design for all screen sizes
- Smooth animations and transitions

## Browser Support

- Chrome (latest)
- Firefox (latest)
- Safari (latest)
- Edge (latest)
- Mobile browsers

## Known Issues

None at this time.

